INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3900','letter','1782-04-02','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','John','Laurens','','individual','','It appears the enemy have it in contemplation to attack us in our divided state; they must inevitably ruin us. You will join the army, therefore, without loss of time.','ltr_nag3900.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3901','letter','1782-04-08','Dorchester','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','Lieut. Col. Laurens joined us the night before last, and I have heard nothing further of the enemy\'s attack upon us.','ltr_nag3901.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3902','letter','1782-04-10','Dorchester','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','Lieut. Colonel Laurens has given me an account of the enemy\'s last movement, and Gen. Leslie has explained the object to me in a letter','ltr_nag3902.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3903','letter','1782-04-10','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Peter','Horry','','individual','','I cannot decide on one part of your letter, that is, respecting half-pay. If you were entitled to half-pay on your former standing, you are entitled to it now; but, if you mean upon the present reduction proposed, there can be no half-pay','ltr_nag3903.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3904','letter','1782-04-12','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I have been of opinion some time, and got intelligence last evening, that the enemy were preparing to come out and attack us. It seems the refugees are pushing the General very hard for the purpose.','ltr_nag3904.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3905','letter','1782-04-14','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','The prospect of a general action is not so immediate as I expected a few days ago. You will, therefore, halt in the neighborhood of Strawberry Ferry','ltr_nag3905.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3906','letter','1782-04-15','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I wrote you yesterday to return to Strawberry, but, as you are so near, before you return I wish to see you, provided you come to Mr. Blake\'s to-night','ltr_nag3906.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3907','letter','1782-04-16','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I know of no way of reinforcing you but by Col. Hampton\'s corps. I will speak with the Governor on the subject. At present, I believe we have no spare arms','ltr_nag3907.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3908','letter','1782-04-28','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','We have had no small uneasiness in our camp for want of pay, clothing and spirits. The discontent has reached the enemy, and it is confidently asserted that they are coming out to take advantage of it.','ltr_nag3908.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3909','letter','1782-07-09','Cattles Plantation','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','Nothing reflects more honor upon an officer than accomplishing that by address which others could effect only by force; to save the effusion of human blood must be the wish of every humane and generous bosom.','ltr_nag3909.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3910','letter','1782-07-30','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I am afraid you will now arrive too late to be of any service, unless the goods should be got up the rivers, and your force deter the enemy from following them.','ltr_nag3910.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3911','letter','1782-08-09','Ashley','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I am sorry the enemy is so situated as to give them an opportunity to carry off the produce of the country, without your having it in your power to injure them.','ltr_nag3911.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3912','letter','1782-08-10','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Peter','Horry','','individual','','The dissolution of your corps, or rather embodying it with other corps, I think a prudent measure. At present, I have no commands which will interfere with your wishes for retiring.','ltr_nag3912.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3913','letter','1782-08-24','Ashley','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I have been informed that a fleet, consisting of one sloop-of-war, three galleys, three armed brigs, with ten empty sloops and schooners, having 500 infantry under Major Brewerton and Doyle on board, passed the bar of Charlestown early yesterday morning','ltr_nag3913.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3914','letter','1782-08-29','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','John','Matthews','','individual','','The enemy landed in considerable force. The Colonel\'s party being small, was beat back, in which conflict the Colonel fell','ltr_nag3914.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3915','letter','1782-08-31','Ashley','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','I most sincerely congratulate you upon the very honorable check you gave the enemy, and I am happy to hear you give such ample testimony to the bravery and firmness of the militia.','ltr_nag3915.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3916','letter','1782-09-15','Ashley','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','Intelligence from town induces me to believe the enemy are making preparations for another expedition after provision, and that the neighborhood of Georgetown will be their object','ltr_nag3916.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
INSERT INTO media VALUES ('ltr_nag3917','letter','1782-10-30','','SC','US','Nathanael','Greene','','Francis','Marion','','individual','','Capt. Warren has written to you requesting the prisoners, mentioned in the list you enclosed, might be sent to Charlestown','ltr_nag3917.txt','hans@broughdesign.com',NULL,Now(),NULL,'Documentary History of the American Revolution Consisting of Letters and Papers Relating to the Contest for Liberty, Chiefly in South Carolina, from Originals in the Possession of the Editor, and Other Sources, 1776');
